These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
House: victorian, cape-cod, colonial, art-deco
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. the cape-cod house is between the victorian house and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the art-deco house and the victorian house##7
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| House   | colonial | art-deco       | cape-cod | victorian        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
House: farmhouse, cottage, modern, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the modern house##7
2. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
3. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the cottage house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| House     | modern | cottage       | gothic-revival         | farmhouse     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
City: marseilles, hannover, prague, boston
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to marseilles##7
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the person traveling to boston and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| City   | prague | marseilles  | boston   | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, prince, vegafina, old-henry
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Cigar   | prince      | oliveros   | vegafina | old-henry  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
City: rome, edinburgh, liverpool, hannover
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| City   | rome      | edinburgh | hannover      | liverpool |

