.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, lizard, chinchilla
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, indonesian, nigerian
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the nigerian is somewhere between the american and the dutch##7
7. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Pet      | mouse | rat      | lizard | chinchilla     |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian |

