.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, aristoff, davidoff, ritmeester
1. the argentine is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
3. the spanish is the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Cigar           | davidoff   | ritmeester    | prince       | aristoff  |

