.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
House: wooden, tower, ranch-style, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, r&b, techno
1. the wooden house is not the fan of classical##6
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
4. the wooden house is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the ranch-style house is somewhere between the fan of techno and the tower house##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| House           | gothic-revival | wooden | ranch-style | tower |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | r&b      | classical | pop            |

