.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, turquise, ivory, purple
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person who likes purple##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the person who likes ivory##6
3. the person who likes turquise is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person who likes coral##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Color           | coral    | turquise   | purple  | ivory      |

