.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, mystery
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, august, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching documentary movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation | documentary | epic   |
| Birthday   | march    | august      | may      | july |

