2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the art-deco house##1
3. the farmhouse house is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the gothic-revival house##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the art-deco house and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5

