.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip, daisy, sunflower
1. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
2. the person who growssunflower is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who growsdaisy##7
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
4. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | cola   | mirinda | fanta | water   |
| Flower   | poppy | daisy   | sunflower | tulip |

