4. the spanish is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the trike is not the american##6
6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the french and the american##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Nationality   | spanish | american | thai      | french |
| Transport     | trike  | skateboard  | motorbike | boat   |

