.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, monopoly, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person playing canasta##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Game         | canasta    | monopoly | backgammon     | mah-jongg |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 